message.content:
Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>AI Codex – Negozio di Programmazione AI</title>
    <style>
        * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'system-ui, 'Segoe UI, sans-serif;
    }

        body {
        background: #000;
        color: #lighter;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20;
    }

    .page {
        max-width: 120;
        width: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient circle at 10% 10%, #0a0f1e 0%, #0a0f1e 100%;
        border: 1 solid #0ff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40 #0ff2;
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 12;
        backdrop-filter: blur(2);
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .hero {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 3.2rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing:  -2px;
        background: linear-gradient 45deg, #f0f, #cyan, #0ff);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20 #0ff;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .hero p {
        color: #b0b0ff;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        border-right: 2 solid #0ff;
        border-left: 2 solid #0ff;
        padding: 0 20;
        display: inline-block;
        letter-spacing: 2;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5 #0ff;
    }

    .card-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .card {
        background: #0a0f1e;
        border: 1 solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 8;
        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        transition: 0.2s;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10 #0ff2;
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 0 20 #0ff;
        border-color: #f0f;
    }

    .card h3 {
        color: #f0f;
        margin-bottom: 0.5;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .card p {
        color: #ddd;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .form-area {
        background: #0a0f1e;
        border: 1 solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 8;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10 #0ff2;
    }

    .form-area h2 {
        color: #f0f;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        letter-spacing: 1;
    }

    .form-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.2;
    }

    .form-row input,
    .form-row textarea {
        background: #0002;
        border: 1 solid #cyan;
        border-radius: 4;
        padding: 0.8 0.6;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #fff;
        outline: none;
        transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .form-row input:focus,
    .form-row textarea:focus {
        border-color: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 8 #f0f;
    }

    .form-row label {
        color: #b0b0ff;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 1;
    }

    .btn {
        background: #0ff2;
        border: 1 solid #0ff;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 0.8 1.2;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 4;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.2s;
        margin-top: 1.2;
        width: 100%;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background: #f0f;
        color: #000;
        border-color: #f0f;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20 #f0f;
    }

    .footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #888;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        border-top: 1 solid #0ff2;
        padding-top: 1.5;
        margin-top: 1.5;
    }

    .footer a {
        color: #0ff;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .popup-over {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: #0007;
        backdrop-filter: blur(2);
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        z-index: 100;
    }

    .popup-over.show {
        display: flex;
    }

    .popup-box {
        background: #0a0f1e;
        border: 2 solid #0ff;
        border-radius: 12;
        padding: 2.5 3;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40 #0ff;
        animation: flick 0.3s;
    }

    .popup-box h2 {
        color: #f0f;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5;
    }

    .popup-box p {
        color: #ddd;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .popup-box .btn {
        width: auto;
        margin: 1.5 auto 0;
        padding: 0.5 2;
        background: #f0f;
        color: #000;
        border: none;
    }

    .popup-box .btn:hover {
        background: #fff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600) {
        .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.2;
    }
    .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .page {
        padding: 1.5;
    }
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>AI Codex</h1>
            <p>Negozio di Programmazione AI</p>
        </section>

        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>⚔ Synth</h3>
                <p>Modelli preduttivi per reti neurali</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>⚡ Neural</h3>
                <p>API di inferenza quantistica</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🌀 Deep</h3>
                <p>Alogeni di apprendimento profondo</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-area">
            <h2>⚛ Contt. Cyber</h2>
            <form id="contactForm">
                <div class="form-row">
                    <label for="name">Nome</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Il tuo nome" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-row">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="tu@dominio.com" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-row">
                    <label for="message">Messaggio</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Scta la tua richiesta..." required></textarea>
                </div>
                <button class="btn" type="submit" id="submitBtn">Invia Richiesta</button>
                <div style="false" id="errorMessage" style="color:#b0b0ff;"></div>
           form>
        </div>

        <footer class="footer">
            <span>⚤ 2020 | AI Codex | <a href="#">Termi</a></span>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <!-- popup-over id="popupOver" class="popup-over">
        <div class="popup-box">
            <h2>⚡ Richiesta Inviata</h2>
            <p>Il tuo messaggio è stato recato nella rete cyber.</p>
            <button class="btn" id="popupClose">OK</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const form = document.getElementById('contactForm');
        const popup = document.getElementById('popupOver');
        const closeBtn = document.getElementById('popupClose');
        const errorDiv = document.getElementById('errorMessage');

        form.onsubmit = function (e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            if errorDiv && errorDiv.textContent = '';
            const name = document.getElementById('name');
            const email = document.getElementById('email');
            const message = document.getElementById('message');
            if name.value.trim() === '' || email.value.trim() === '' || message.value.trim() === '' {
                errorDiv.textContent = 'Compila tutti campi!';
                errorDiv.style.color = 'cyan';
                return;
            }
            popup.classList.add('show');
            form.reset();
        };

        closeBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
            popup.classList.remove('show');
        });

        window.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
            if e.target === popup) {
                popup.classList.remove('show');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

